ECONOMIC Freedom Fighters leader Julius Malema says if Parliament Speaker
Baleka Mbete doesn't respond to their request for a Motion Of No Confidence in Zuma, by Tuesday
they will launch an urgent High Court application to force her.Malema says Zuma will be removed and once he is gone, Parliament
has to be dissolved.Meanwhile, the Democratic Alliance, UDM and COPE are just some of the
opposition parties that are part of the opposition meeting in their bid to get
